### Get full world map (public — no auth needed)
# Returns terrain grid + all visible POIs (towns, landmarks)
GET {{host}}/map

### Get full world map (authenticated — includes your discoveries)
GET {{host}}/map
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get all named regions (forests, mountains, swamps, deserts)
GET {{host}}/map/regions

### Get cell info — Thornhaven (starting town at 25,24)
GET {{host}}/map/cell/25/24

### Get cell info — ocean tile (0,0)
GET {{host}}/map/cell/0/0

### Get cell info — authenticated (shows your discoveries)
GET {{host}}/map/cell/25/24
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
